---

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section
    class="py-20 px-6 md:px-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#a5b4fc]/20 to-[#c4b5fd]/20 rounded-3xl my-8 mx-4 md:mx-12"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Ready to Transform Your <span class="text-primary-dark"
          >Productivity?</span
        >
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join thousands of professionals who've reclaimed their focus and
        enhanced their productivity with Flipside Brain.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="#"
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-[#818cf8] hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-bold rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all text-center"
        >
          Start Your Free Trial
        </a>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="px-8 py-4 border border-gray-200 hover:border-[#818cf8] text-gray-700 font-bold rounded-full shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all text-center"
        >
          Book a Demo
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
          Frequently Asked <span class="text-primary-dark">Questions</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Find answers to common questions about Flipside Brain.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">
            How does Flipside Brain help with focus?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Flipside Brain combines website blocking, distraction tracking,
            focus timers, and analytics to help you identify and eliminate
            productivity leaks while building better work habits.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">
            Can I use Flipside Brain on multiple devices?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes! Flipside Brain syncs across all your devices including desktop,
            laptop, tablet, and mobile phones, ensuring a consistent experience
            everywhere you work.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Is my data private and secure?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Absolutely. We take data privacy seriously and never sell your
            information. All your productivity data is encrypted and used only
            to provide you with insights to improve your focus.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">
            Can I customize the website blocker?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Yes, the Pro and Team plans offer highly customizable website
            blocking. You can create different blocking profiles for various
            work modes, schedule automatic blocking times, and set exceptions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>